             </div><br/>
             <div class="col-sm-5 col-md-6 main">
<div><h3>
        Choose where your Featured {{ hairtype | capitalize }} Hair Ad will appear.</h3><br/> For example, if you wanted your
    Featured hair to appear on the Malaysian 18 Inch Wavy Hair's page in the wizard you would make those selections.
    <br/>After Choosing Your Hair type, Selecting the Inch and Style continue through the wizard.
    <br/>Next,Upload your Featured Hair's Picture, set its Title along with its Ad Summary and Price within "Describe your Item and List Your Price" Section.
    <br/><br/>Finally, complete the "Select the Ad Position" you wish your Featured Hair to appear in.
</div><br/><br/>
                 <div id="clickHairChoice"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Choose Hair</button></div>

                 <div id="hairChoiceForm" class="well well-lg"><b>Hair Type:</b> {{ hairtype | capitalize }} </div>

                 <div id="clickInchStyleChoice"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Select Inch and Style</button></div>

                 <div id="inchStyleChoiceForm" class="well well-lg" style="display: none">
                     {{ form_start(form) }}
                     {{ form_errors(form) }}

                     {{ form_row(form.inch) }}
                     {{ form_row(form.style) }}


                     </div>

                 <div id="clickUploadPicture"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Upload Picture</button></div>

                 <div id="uploadPictureForm" class="well well-lg" style="display: none">{{ form_row(form.featuredHairPic) }}</div>

                 <div id="clickItemDetails"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Describe Your Item and List its Price</button></div>

                 <div id="itemDetailsForm" class="well well-lg" style="display: none">

                     {{ form_row(form.featuredHairHeading) }}
                     {{ form_row(form.featuredHairSummary) }}
                     {{ form_row(form.featuredHairPrice) }}

                    </div>

                 <div id="clickHairVendor"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Hair Vendor's Name</button></div>

                 <div id="hairVendorForm" class="well well-lg" style="display: none">
                     {{ form_errors(form) }}
                     {{ form_row(form.featuredHairVendor) }}
                 </div>

                 <div id="clickAdPosition"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Select The Ad Position</button></div>

                 <div id="adPositionForm" class="well well-lg" style="display: none">

                     {{ form_errors(form) }}

                     {{ form_row(form.featuredHairPosition) }}
                     {{ form_end(form) }}



                 </div>
<br/><br/>
                 <div id="clickReviewAd"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" disabled>Review and Confirm</button></div>






             </div>
     <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4 main">
         <div class="progress">
             <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="20"
                  aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width:20%">
                 20% Complete (success)
<br/>

             </div>
         </div>

